<h1>Applications</h1>
<p>
One of the first things people ask about anything is: <i>What is it used for</i>? 
Tetration is no different, but since its applications are few and far between,
it is a difficult task to collect them all.
As we learn more about tetration, we find that it has more and more applications, 
and that its place in pure mathematics may come into question very soon. 
This is because researchers are finding applications of tetration all the time. 
For example, these are a few applications listed here:
